{"tid":120684,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"有種浪漫叫陳柏宇","createTime":"2017-02-14T15:16:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-17T12:40:39.000Z","uid":2265,"like":107,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"276c51511fbef0b46f90af721017172c11ab2dc1","tid":120684,"uid":2265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T15:16:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://image.joox.com/JOOXcover/0/27f0a0c3f553b877/640\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimage.joox.com%2FJOOXcover%2F0%2F27f0a0c3f553b877%2F640&h=c480f599&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>有種浪漫叫陳柏宇</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n浪漫不一定是粉紅色吧，我要說的，是輕熟男的浪漫。 陳柏宇，常被喻為港式「療癒系情歌王子」，出道10年，首首情歌到肉感人，用心聽，不難發現當中的演進，由初出道的青澀沉溺，逐步走到新碟《The Player》的半熟寬大，從「無言的親親親／侵襲我心」到「沒有你／我什麼都不是」，情路縱然曲折，但終究會成長，近年他更讓大家叫回他真名陳廣偉，決心做自己。難怪好多男生都聽陳柏宇，由𡃁仔聽到變中佬，由單拖聽到甩拖，首首都在K房裡爭著唱，只因陳氏情歌總讓人找到共鳴。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://image.joox.com/JOOXcover/0/588eeda01a38492b/640\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimage.joox.com%2FJOOXcover%2F0%2F588eeda01a38492b%2F640&h=a5173f96&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">「感覺 加倍念記／嘴裡 那份甜味」</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n不少人也從苦情的〈固執〉一曲開始認識Jason，收錄於首張大碟《First Experience》中的〈永久保存〉則是他的大熱廣告歌。Jason以他擅長R&amp;B曲風，展現青春甜蜜的一面，旋律輕快，簡單而純真，校園初戀的感覺，返晒嚟。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">「相愛憑幾公里飛馳 要停下回望太遲」</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n數男人味頗重的一首情歌，要說〈車匙〉。一架車，承載多少戀愛回憶？「手中緊握車匙 追不到往事」，歌詞雖然單刀直入，K歌旋律卻好易入腦。「有時情路裡太多標誌」，陳少琪的詞，填滿感情迷茫的心事，這些年，多少男生開著車，邊聽邊追悔。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://image.joox.com/JOOXcover/0/ae76c660136c2557/640\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimage.joox.com%2FJOOXcover%2F0%2Fae76c660136c2557%2F640&h=7d2c4445&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">「無言的親親親／侵襲我心」</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n夕爺揪心的詞，陳光榮極易入口的曲，讓Jason唱出深陷三角戀的無奈，造就最經典的慘情K歌，副歌一段的假音，K房裡叫男生力竭聲嘶地唱，2009年他更憑此曲首度入圍叱咤我最喜愛歌曲五強。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">「時光給我的傷害 就當是愛」</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n看不見未來的感情，不捨也要割捨的心酸，譜出這首異地戀情歌，鋼琴伴奏與Jason的柔情演繹產生了很微妙的化學作用，讓此曲也榮獲四台冠軍歌。比以往的慘情歌，歌詞中多了一份成熟，「如果想到我的話／要笑著來當我在原地」，要學懂愛，先學懂放開，誰知道年月過去，告別以後，曾熱戀過的人還會不會有緣再聚。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://image.joox.com/JOOXcover/0/c4b765a6aa3eead1/640\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimage.joox.com%2FJOOXcover%2F0%2Fc4b765a6aa3eead1%2F640&h=f8ea589e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><br />\n「我現時自己肯做飯／悶極時自己可浪漫」</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n喝水行山、整理床單、自己煮飯，填詞人陳詠謙從平實日常，側寫一個男人努力地過著單身生活，卻偶然驚覺睹物便思人，對痛失而久的前度暗自追悔的故事。有過去的男人，一定能聽懂。好兄弟林奕匡作曲，讓Jason挑戰高難度音域，豐富編曲也讓他展示由細膩到激情的唱功。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">「奇妙的生命／多得你跨出腳印」</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n係人都知Jason毫不避忌放閃，此曲表面是對女友不離不棄唱出感謝之情，大路澎拜但感人，弦樂部份更找來捷克國家交響樂團現場演奏錄製，華麗之中也見真誠，幾乎一聽就覺得是求婚或婚禮上的必備飲歌。而其實他想感謝的，何止女友，還有在音樂路上與他一起成長的忠粉。好多人替Jason紅歌唔紅人而不值，他卻總是沒有怨言，還說自己喜歡當配角。陳柏宇，就是有種默默耕耘、不肯放棄的浪漫。「如果一個等／如何有這種犯錯的勇敢，唯有你企得很近」，正正道盡十年來他對支持者的感激。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://image.joox.com/JOOXcover/0/6fc26474d3d7ed87/640\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimage.joox.com%2FJOOXcover%2F0%2F6fc26474d3d7ed87%2F640&h=fe6e9381&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: right;\">編輯：Choman02/08/2017</div><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.joox.com/hk/zh/?page=p2preplay&amp;lang=zh_TW&amp;area=hk&amp;videoid=100126504&amp;voovid=40647#/music_detail?id=693&amp;type=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.joox.com%2Fhk%2Fzh%2F%3Fpage%3Dp2preplay%26lang%3Dzh_TW%26area%3Dhk%26videoid%3D100126504%26voovid%3D40647%23%2Fmusic_detail%3Fid%3D693%26type%3D1&d=Q0Uk0WlElUZ8hxv%2Fjb96JwhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=4eabf9ca\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.joox.com/hk/zh/?page=p2preplay&amp;lang=zh_TW&amp;area=hk&amp;videoid=100126504&amp;voovid=40647#/music_detail?id=693&amp;type=1</a>"},{"pid":"b3774684f401881d23ba38ba54860dac078f242c","tid":120684,"uid":2265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T15:18:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d34aa6054f124195dd2c2b03275ab75929e3a9e","tid":120684,"uid":16730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T15:22:15.000Z","msg":"我愛你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"876edd7e8e04579954a9cbb3be02f8a24cd4d8a9","tid":120684,"uid":2265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T15:25:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我愛你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d58194ba45c5afebd79827219758853e222f432b","tid":120684,"uid":2265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T15:29:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e00e6d80b379c4cdcb9ea8721a8ef20f888a3b22","tid":120684,"uid":46042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T15:29:58.000Z","msg":"淨係記得l miss you"},{"pid":"a8edc00f43c2c88eb803f2331e291e2aa06f9407","tid":120684,"uid":27416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T15:30:20.000Z","msg":"無逸後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"855de9f36dcd1b66c9c396546646b34997ec1950","tid":120684,"uid":2265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T15:30:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>淨係記得l miss you</blockquote><br />\n經典<br />\nI miss you 感動你"},{"pid":"806e68559ae0440b0662a661a13ed05ce9b7a3ed","tid":120684,"uid":2265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T15:30:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無逸後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n逸後 正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac1d07e76f35ef2506d44737ee4b70f610011baf"